 place, mix again <b>10 sec\/speed 7<b>."},{"content":"With wet hands, form 24 golf ball-sized meatballs then transfer to Varoma dish and tray then set aside. Clean and dry mixing bowl then prepare sauce."},{"isHeader":true,"content":"Sauce"},{"content":"Place garlic and oil in mixing bowl then chop <b>8 sec\/speed 5<b>. Sauté <b>3 min\/Varoma\/speed 1<b>."},{"content":"Add green peppers, red peppers, chilli sauce, tomatoes, white wine, water, tomato purée, Tabasco and remaining 1 tsp salt. Place covered Varoma into position and steam <b>30 min\/Varoma\/\/speed 2<b>. Remove Varoma, transfer meatballs to a serving bowl and cover with cling film to keep warm."},{"content":"Add black beans to sauce and cook <b>3 min\/Varoma\/\/speed <b>. Pour sauce over meatballs and sprinkle with reserved parsley. Serve with your choice of rice, pasta or potatoes."}],"hintsAndTricks":["This dish would also work well as part of a tapas selection. Allow 1-2 meatballs per person."],"basicInfo":["medium","30m","1h 5m","6 portions"]}